# Decision Documentation Enforcement

Whenever a design or product decision is introduced, changed, or finalized, update `docs/code-first-nav-and-graph-views.md` in the same session.

For each decision, document:
- what changed,
- why it was chosen,
- impacted areas/files,
- follow-ups or open questions.

This rule applies to:
- Design OS application decisions (`src/`),
- product planning/export decisions (`product/`, `product-plan/`).
